	* INSTALL: fix generation of UTF8 locales
	* PRE_INSTALL: make /lib/ld-linux.so.2|/lib/ld.so.1 point to the ld.so
	  in the now built glibc so it doesn't break when the old ld.so is
	  removed during dispel

